  <brief_title>Surgical or Conservative Treatment of Sportsman Hernia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Chronic Groin Pain and Sportsman Hernia of Athletes: Randomized Study Between Conservative Treatment and Laparoscopic Hernioplasty (TEP)</official_title>
